tourBios.carHigh:
2015:Played on both the Asian Tour and the Asian Development Tour. At the Ambassador ADT in May, a 54-hole event, he tied for sixth with back-to-back 70s over his final round that left him a distant 10 shots short of PGA TOUR China Series' regular Shih Chang Chan. 

2014: Attempted to qualify for the PGA TOUR China Series but finished T55 at the first Qualifying Tournament in ShenzhenâŚSuccessfully Monday-qualified and made his Series debut in mid-June, at the Earls Beijing Open. Opened 68-72 then reversed his scores, shooting 72-68 over his final 36 holes to T19. The finish was the best performance by a Monday qualifier to date. In his first-round 68, became the second player to record two eagles in the same round when he eagled the 11th and 18th holes at Earls Beijing GC in the first round.

dyn.dynResults: He has finished 19th on the PGA Tour China Serie 2 times.
